text: Tímea Benkô is a Hungarian water polo player. She was a member of the Hungarian women's national water polo team. She played at the 2002 Water Polo World Cup, 2005 World Aquatics Championships, and 2007 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Timea Benko of Hungary in action in the Women's Bronze Medal Water Polo match getty * Hungary's Timea Benko (blue cap) is detained by Canada's Ann Dow during their women's water polo semifinal match getty Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Hungarian water polo players
